column5: Just joined the site. Here is a pair of early ice splake.
Very nice fish!!!  Looks like the bottom one had a terrible hemorrhoid.
Couple nice fish. Welcome to the site and what part of the country are you from?

Smokey I am in Muskoka Ontario and fish mainly Lake Trout and Brookies but pickerel (walleye) are not out of the question either. Looks like a very Fun site here and am glad I stumbled upon it. These were caught in mid December.
Very nice fish there!!! Welcome to the board as well.
One more pic of the ice conditions. There was 5+ inches of ice but very slushy that day.
Welcome s5, a couple nice fatties...
welcome to the board and congrats on the catch
Nice ones - welcome to the board!
